      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
