      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone rigorous inspection with documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The suspension retains factory kinematics with no bushing deflection or damper fatigue. Finished in concours-level Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle maintains original paint depth and factory tolerances throughout. A definitive driver\u2019s car for the technical purist.",
